      "title": "Furnace oil low notification",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Society of Electrical Engineers reports that the supply of furnace oil essential to power plants is running low.",
        "For this, the Association has mentioned that only the fuel required for a day is in stock in the integrated network of Kalanitissa Power Plant.",
        "The 2 generators of the Sapugaskanda power plant have enough furnace oil for only 4 days.",
        "Also, the Society of Electrical Engineers said that the West Terminal Power Plant has 2 days' worth of furnace oil in stock. (R)"
      ],
